===Etymology===
{{term|hello|Hello}} (first attested in 1846) from {{term|hallo}} (attested 1840), from {{term|holla}}, {{term|hollo}} (attested 1588). This variant of {{term|hallo}} is often credited to [[w:Thomas Edison|Thomas Edison]] as a coinage for telephone use, but its appearance in print predates the invention of the telephone by several decades.

Possibly from the {{OHG.}} & {{OS.}} verb {{term|halôn, holôn||to bring something, to gather}}, akin to {{E.}} {{term|hale}} or {{term|hail}}.

